      <title>捷克总理希望以更快的步伐降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/czech-premier-favors-faster-pace-of-interest-rate-cuts-than-seen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克总理彼得·菲亚拉周日表示，他赞成这个中欧国家以比目前预期更快的速度实施货币宽松政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/czech-premier-favors-faster-pace-of-interest-rate-cuts-than-seen</guid>
